title: Didn't get the honor 5 ward.
body:
I just got the end of season rewards but Im honor 5 and didn't get the honor 5 reward for some reason.

Screenshots: https://imgur.com/a/RXXEoUK

replies.body: Were you Honour 5 at the time season ended (Nov 14th) or did you reach 5 after? To earn Honour 5 rewards you had to be Honour 5 on season end, not on reward redemption.
I am in the same boat here. I don't log in that often, so I logged in today and was told I was lvl 5 but I am missing the lvl 5 ward.
